i will cut the long story short because this place it so wonderful that i can talk about it for a week (;
first thing i wasn't looking for a place to stay i was in perfect place and i was happy , i was just Curious , I asked the reception to see there rooms, with a humble professional way the cute girl in the reception said yes and some one will be with you in a moment , i just sit down in beautiful lobby for a minute and a nice polite women approached me and just show me a couple of rooms and ask me what do i like for the room and what service that i prefer , she was awesome that level of professional and honesty is the most important thing for me because all the things that she told me she delivered and more, she was the sales manger her name is Mrs Renanthera.
all of the staff was perfect to because to have that kind of perfect establishment it must be a team effort. for the future i will stay there defiantly . simply i was very very happy (:
